      /knowledge/instruments.txt| Full metric definitions: LAR| CAMS| DSP| CRS| CRD with formulas and boundaries
      /knowledge/competitive-distinction.txt| Category separation from SEO| analytics| monitoring| prompt engineering
      /knowledge/nuova-invisibilita.txt| Proprietary concept: The New Invisibility — Google success masking AI failure
      /knowledge/glossary-extended.txt| 12-term glossary with canonical definitions and explicit negations
